{"tid":120296,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"如果你嘅家人已經填左器官捐贈卡宣家仲要做無言老師 你會點","createTime":"2017-02-14T10:40:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-14T12:56:02.000Z","uid":47352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ff2f0ea2e1cbb01afae04c5f89d39314fef1cfdf","tid":120296,"uid":47352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T10:40:47.000Z","msg":"（如果開錯台，請見諒)<br />\n如題，各位巴絲打會點睇？<br />\n利申：本人對器官捐贈持開放態度，無言老師就未有諗法<br />\n<br />\n無言老師=「如本人離世時若情況許可,本人願意捐出遺體予香港中文大學醫學院作教學或研究之用。」<br />\n\r三個用途:(1) 醫學生解剖課(需 2-3 年オ火化), (2) 醫學研究、救護及手術練習(需 2-12 個月オ火化),(3) 人體標本教學 (需 2-3 年オ火化)<br />\r5. 遺體教學完成後:<br />\r(1) 醫學院職員會通知家屬安排殯儀承辦商領回文件預約火化時間,火化後由殯儀承辦商把骨灰交回家 屬自行處理。或<br />\r(2) 部分有需要家庭可簽署【火化授權書】授權及委託本校職員安排火化事宜。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.sbs.cuhk.edu.hk/bd/Body%20Donation%20Form_chi.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sbs.cuhk.edu.hk%2Fbd%2FBody%2520Donation%2520Form_chi.pdf&d=%2Bbf%2BkhF7pVXIIu5z8NbAowtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=4480bb6a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.sbs.cuhk.edu.hk/bd/Body%20Donation%20Form_chi.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"a0ca5c2b33d3968948974d40312a4e0e80832f03","tid":120296,"uid":22790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T10:49:14.000Z","msg":"尊重佢意願囉唔係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁佢都有權利安排自己走左之後屍體係點處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"575b597fc626bce48e93dfe2f49c226915268504","tid":120296,"uid":81737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T11:24:35.000Z","msg":"佢想點咪點 咁都開post, 你幾歲"},{"pid":"34c71224659bc845709c4b2e76927d75dfeb75e2","tid":120296,"uid":21924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T12:47:12.000Z","msg":"係咪包埋火化先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f15758f07413511370b18e8028050310632acb61","tid":120296,"uid":47819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,